{"tid":692977,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"牛b死了","createTime":"2018-06-07T05:55:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-05T09:45:24.000Z","uid":7206,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1209f8928300d57e36baf52a9b4d7b1438f411ef","tid":692977,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T05:55:20.000Z","msg":"荃灣大帽山道今早揭發懷疑殘殺小牛的案件。早上10時22分，警方接報有可疑人在大帽山雷達站拖著一隻牛下山，於是派員到場調查，警車駛至大帽山道一處路邊，駭然發現一頭未成年牛隻的屍體，被人掛在路邊的標距柱上，離地約1米，死狀恐怖，於是通知愛護動物協會人員到場協助，CID亦著手調查，列虐待動物案件處理。<br />\n<br />\n疑遭殘殺的小牛屍體，身長一米、高半米，頭部及四肢仍在，但整個腹部被劏開，內臟全被挖空。由於現場附近未發現大量血迹及內臟，不排除小牛遭人殺害後，再掛屍現場標距柱上。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息指，事發時有山上工程人員，發現一名南亞裔男子拖著一隻小牛下山，形迹可疑，於是報警，不排除可疑人見事敗，於是將小牛棄屍，然後登上一輛黑色Audi私家車離開，警方正展開追查。小牛被棄屍的位置，跟離雷達站約10分鐘步程。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180607/58288390\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180607%2F58288390&d=R949l7d43WBU2XNm%2FySWvcP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=5139cab4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180607%2F58288390&h=f7971379\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180607/58288390</a>"},{"pid":"d66cd4bcde80dd58fec6b96e8ae5b576f76999a5","tid":692977,"uid":48577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T05:59:50.000Z","msg":"這個真牛B"},{"pid":"eface5438a1b1cad419e879528fd6c022eb283fc","tid":692977,"uid":7615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T06:12:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0888a2dc3d802197925720ad812050218c411c74","tid":692977,"uid":608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T06:19:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5d3439ec1e2b33024940cd8638927a9d967ac93","tid":692977,"uid":79979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s